INTRODUCTION
Play Pac-man Rush on your Google Chrome Browser with our simple & lightweight extension - No Internet required, no ADS, and 100% Free!

HOW TO INSTALL?
1. Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension
2. Pin the Pac-man Rush extension icon to the Chrome toolbar
3. Click the Pac-man Rush icon on the Chrome toolbar, the Pac-man Rush popup will open. 
That's all you need to do! Have fun!

HOW TO PLAY?
Click on screen to change the Pac-man's direction. Avoid obstacles and collect points.
